and nasty and cruel...

99
00:05:20,038 --> 00:05:22,540
Enough with the lessons!
This isn't a school!

100
00:05:22,574 --> 00:05:24,242
(neck cracks)

101
00:05:26,211 --> 00:05:30,481
♪ Once a year
we are not hungry ♪

102
00:05:30,515 --> 00:05:34,819
