208
00:10:25,137 --> 00:10:28,072
So, in conclusion,
my show-and-tell is...

209
00:10:28,106 --> 00:10:29,574
this!

210
00:10:29,608 --> 00:10:32,643
Excellent, Lisa.
A-plus.

211
00:10:32,678 --> 00:10:34,045
Bart, your turn.

212
00:10:34,079 --> 00:10:37,882
Well, my show-and-tell is
that I'm on Lisa's body.

213
00:10:37,916 --> 00:10:39,550
