plus all the sawdust he can eat.

400
00:17:22,514 --> 00:17:24,148
Well, you've got
an emerald ring.

401
00:17:25,651 --> 00:17:26,851
My mother's ring.

402
00:17:26,885 --> 00:17:27,852
(sobs)

403
00:17:27,886 --> 00:17:29,821
